                                                   rdfs:range <https://w3id.org/cpm-arch/cpm/CP20_Construction_Work> ;
                                                   rdfs:comment "This property allows to relate an instance of CP 20 Construction Work to an instance of CP1 Built Entity. It intends to describe the relation between a construction element and an architecture work or part of it when they are in a condition of mutual interference. Particularly this property allows to describe the condition of a construction element intersecting a building or part of, as for example a lintel intersecting the apse of a church or a trace to realise electric system intersecting a wall." ;
                                                   rdfs:label "is crossed by" ;
                                                   <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "Pc63" .


