###  https://w3id.org/cpm-arch/cpm/Pc69_shows_as_construction_element_singular
<https://w3id.org/cpm-arch/cpm/Pc69_shows_as_construction_element_singular> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                                                            owl:inverseOf <https://w3id.org/cpm-arch/cpm/Pc69i_is_construction_element_singular_of> ;
