                                                    rdfs:comment "This property documents that an instance of CP42 Material Decay was made possible by a specific E3 Condition State. It refers to the need to describe, beyond the causes of a particular state of degradation due to specific factors such as dampness as an example, the environmental agents such as climate or exposition that are described through the class condition state." ;
                                                    rdfs:label "was fostered by" ;
                                                    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "Pc6" .


